    <edge source="Quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh c&#7911;a T&#242;a &#225;n tuy&#234;n b&#7889; m&#7897;t ng&#432;&#7901;i l&#224; &#273;&#227; ch&#7871;t" target="&#7910;y ban nh&#226;n d&#226;n c&#7845;p x&#227;">
