    <edge source="&#272;I&#7872;U 202 (B&#7896; LU&#7852;T LAO &#272;&#7896;NG 2019)" target="QUY&#7870;T &#272;&#7882;NH &#272;I&#7872;U 202 (B&#7896; LU&#7852;T LAO &#272;&#7896;NG 2019)">
      <data key="d0">Quy &#273;&#7883;nh v&#7873; n&#7897;i dung c&#7911;a quy&#7871;t &#273;&#7883;nh &#273;&#236;nh c&#244;ng</data>
